<div class="story">
<p>The Currituck Club is a 585 acre sound front gated community in Corolla stretching for 3 miles along the Currituck Sound. The Currituck Club is made up of 4 smaller communities  including <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/corolla/magnolia-bay.asp" title="Magnolia Bay">Magnolia Bay</a>, <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/corolla/the-hammocks.asp" title="The Hammocks">The Hammocks</a>, and <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/corolla/windswept-ridge.asp" title="Windswept Ridge">Windswept Ridge</a> plus the main body which is The Currituck Club. An 18 hole golf course is spread out through the community with some of the holes situated along the sound front. Other amenities include pools, clubhouse, tennis and a trolley that runs to the beach access and back. There is an active HOA which takes care of all this plus the private roads. </p>
